    "Background": {
      "text": "Third most common primary bone malignancy after\nmultiple myeloma\nand\nosteosarcoma\nAround ninety percent of chondrosarcomas are of low metastatic potential\nOsteochondromas\nand\nenchondromas\ncan be precursors lesions",
